class pynext.RatelimitPayload(retry_after, is_global, route, user=None)[source]#

Bases: object

Dataclass Payload passed in the on_http_ratelimit event.

Parameters:

  • retry_after (float) –

    Time in seconds until ratelimit ends.

    Warning

    Time until ratelimit ends is without additional time given in the PynextClient class.

  • is_global (bool) – Whether ratelimit is global.

  • route (Route) – Blocked http route.

  • user (Optional[SelfBot]) – Selfbot that received ratelimit.

class pynext.EmojisUpdatePayload(guild, added_emojis, deleted_emojis)[source]#

Bases: object

Dataclass Payload passed in the on_guild_emojis_update event.

Parameters:

  • guild (Guild) – Guild on which the payload was received.

  • added_emojis (list[Emoji]) – List with added emojis.

  • deleted_emojis (list[Emoji]) – List with removed emojis.
